org.apache.giraph.partition

接口 ReusesObjectsPartition<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,M extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>

  • 类型参数:
    I - Vertex id
    V - Vertex value
    E - Edge value
    M - Message value
    所有超级接口:
    ImmutableClassesGiraphConfigurable<I,V,E,M>, Iterable<Vertex<I,V,E,M>>, Partition<I,V,E,M>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable
    所有已知实现类:
    ByteArrayPartition

    public interface ReusesObjectsPartition<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,M extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends Partition<I,V,E,M>
    Empty interface to characterize Partition implementations that don't keep references to the Vertex objects they are passed. The Giraph infrastructure can exploit this characteristic by reusing Vertex objects.
